  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, whisk together eggs, sugar, soy sauce, hoisin sauce, sake (if using), and salt until well combined.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together mirin and water until dissolved.",
    "In a steamer basket, place a sheet of parchment paper with a small indentation in the center.",
    "Pour the egg mixture into the indentation and steam for 12 minutes over boiling water or in a steamer set to 180°F (82°C)."
